        <h2 id="firstpost">New Kazakhstan</h2>
        <h6>Posted in 2022 June 13</h6>
        
        <p>This is not only the renewal of the state apparatus, as some experts simplistically imagine. This is primarily a reset of social values. Rejection of radicalism, extreme views and actions, strengthening of the creative motive. Overcoming all kinds of fractures in society. It also means the continuation of gradual and systemic reforms. The humanitarian dimension of state policy and the bet on human capital

